---
import { site } from "../data/site";
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="container article">
    <h2>{site.brand} {site.country}: reusable SEO content section</h2>
    <p>
      This block imitates the long-form content area commonly used on affiliate landing pages.
      In a real production template it could come from Markdown, a CMS, or generated copy reviewed
      by an editor. The goal is to keep the visual layout stable while changing the brand and geo.
    </p>
    <p>
      A practical production workflow separates content from layout. The layout handles typography,
      tables, image spacing and responsive behavior. The content layer handles claims, payment
      methods, bonuses, disclaimers and local wording.
    </p>
    <div class="image-link" role="img" aria-label="Demo banner placeholder">
      <span>{site.brand}</span>
      <strong>{site.country} gaming guide</strong>
    </div>

    <h2>Payment methods and trust signals</h2>
    <p>
      Payment tables are common in this niche because users want quick confirmation that the site
      supports familiar methods. The table below is demo content and should be replaced per market.
    </p>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Method</th>
          <th>Deposit</th>
          <th>Withdrawal</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Visa / Mastercard</td>
          <td>Instant</td>
          <td>1-3 days</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Interac</td>
          <td>Instant</td>
          <td>24 hours</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Bank transfer</td>
          <td>1-2 days</td>
          <td>3-5 days</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>Mobile-first layout</h2>
    <p>
      The template is designed mobile-first because most paid traffic lands on touch devices.
      Important CTAs stay visible without hover, card rows scroll horizontally, and typography
      avoids tiny tap targets.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .article {
    max-width: 920px;
  }

  .article p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1.02rem;
  }

  .image-link {
    display: grid;
    min-height: 220px;
    align-content: end;
    gap: 6px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin: 28px 0;
    padding: 24px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1d4ed8, #7c2d12);
  }

  .image-link span {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.76);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .image-link strong {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  table {
    width: 100%;
    margin: 18px 0 30px;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--panel);
  }

  th,
  td {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 12px;
    text-align: left;
  }

  th {
    color: var(--brand-2);
  }
</style>
